{"tid":757760,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"【飲茶打尖霸王】有片直擊 潮江春部長安排熟客打尖 本刊當場踢爆 (足本版)","createTime":"2018-07-27T06:05:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-27T11:53:51.000Z","uid":171786,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"766d58d13cc0153079b3256b05eb6d18a53c3af5","tid":757760,"uid":171786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T06:05:52.000Z","msg":"往酒樓飲茶，人多時要取籌等位是常識吧。但有讀者向本刊投訴，大埔新達廣場的潮江春，有部長經常私下幫熟客插隊留枱，非常離譜<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n為求真相，記者上週日前往實地視察。咦，一個兩個均是這樣，為何他們均站在後門和收銀處旁？這位咬著芒果乾的大叔，站著等待大約5分鐘，一名女部長就靜俏俏安排入座。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n就是這樣，大叔施施然插隊入座，原本於門口等候的親友，當知道有位後，就大模斯樣會合。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n輪到第二個女茶客站左收銀處旁，她均是沒有取籌，果然不消幾分鐘，她成功插隊入座，一眾親友又很有默契出現，還送贈一盒甜品予得力部長，就當是回禮吧。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如是者，不停有熟客橫手干預，他們均熟悉規矩，最可憐要算是一班乖乖站在門口排隊的食客，記者也嘗試領取二人枱籌號，最終卻要苦等接近一小時。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n及後，由於職員對記者在場內拍攝感到可疑，再不敢幫熟客插隊。此時，一位持柺杖的婆婆站在後門呆等約十分鐘，沒有職員理會她。婆婆表情很無奈，因為記者正靠近她身旁，所以無職員敢上前接觸她，於是婆婆就索性自己出馬霸枱，最後當然失敗而回。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n記者上前踢爆這批茶客和侍應，經理高先生見狀隨即上前勸阻，着茶客不用回應，高經理亦否認提供插隊貴賓式制度。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美心集團就事件回覆本刊，已要求員工應按照相關指引同流程處理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/spot/20180727/608381?utm_campaign=hkad_mag_fullvideo&amp;utm_medium=internal&amp;utm_source=hkad&amp;utm_content=article_text_link\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fspot%2F20180727%2F608381%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_mag_fullvideo%26utm_medium%3Dinternal%26utm_source%3Dhkad%26utm_content%3Darticle_text_link&d=5SQu4Df4Zm6QU7pBGlGX%2BL%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=f37592f6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fspot%2F20180727%2F608381%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_mag_fullvideo%26utm_medium%3Dinternal%26utm_source%3Dhkad%26utm_content%3Darticle_text_link&h=5181d369\" target=\"_blank\">http://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/spot/20180727/608381?utm_campaign=hkad_mag_fullvideo&amp;utm_medium=internal&amp;utm_source=hkad&amp;utm_content=article_text_link</a>"},{"pid":"f676338543b4f8ca4bc21daa9a2d6c23c8e697ca","tid":757760,"uid":6063,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T07:52:09.000Z","msg":"究極魚蛋論"},{"pid":"96d657a09555e916f70bf95c03960928d696b93f","tid":757760,"uid":147079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T08:21:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"78d49eb6bc60f2586e7041d25dcf1701af1a1362","tid":757760,"uid":113675,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T08:27:37.000Z","msg":"全香港都係咁<br />\n<br />\n只不過係另一種形式既VIP<br />\n<br />\n你估過時過節佢地唔洗買返d月餅同年糕咩<br />\n<br />\n條數係返度"},{"pid":"b6bbe01843eb14b29aa8934781a07295010d9b6b","tid":757760,"uid":16343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"96d657a09555e916f70bf95c03960928d696b93f","tid":757760,"uid":147079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T08:21:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T08:30:51.000Z","msg":"I咩cac<br />\n新年封大封利是你吹得佢脹咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9b27251ba057cc8687c487c6b50960280209d3b","tid":757760,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T08:38:16.000Z","msg":"睇死又係大陸人，有鄉音"},{"pid":"2613ad10c6aee7727ca7005106965350ea5efbde","tid":757760,"uid":34286,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T08:41:33.000Z","msg":"正常熟客入先<br />\n無問題"},{"pid":"de91005c5b5b692f81a10c86be16e0d944bfbb7f","tid":757760,"uid":23833,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T08:45:07.000Z","msg":"飲茶文化不嬲都係咁<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n支那特質"},{"pid":"239bf30efa982d816f7e0abdec9d5bdc4f382d89","tid":757760,"uid":11840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"78d49eb6bc60f2586e7041d25dcf1701af1a1362","tid":757760,"uid":113675,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T08:27:37.000Z","msg":"全香港都係咁<br />\n<br />\n只不過係另一種形式既VIP<br />\n<br />\n你估過時過節佢地唔洗買返d月餅同年糕咩<br />\n<br />\n條數係返度"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T08:59:40.000Z","msg":"點只月餅年糕<br />\n親戚D廢老擺生日酒 <br />\n早午晚都係同一間食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"789d9bbe86809d078b633c26892a9ce09ff3f990","tid":757760,"uid":4635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T09:56:38.000Z","msg":"新茶客<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24b57a3e7ee3c18bef38043d2377c36676a960d8","tid":757760,"uid":140363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"239bf30efa982d816f7e0abdec9d5bdc4f382d89","tid":757760,"uid":11840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"78d49eb6bc60f2586e7041d25dcf1701af1a1362","tid":757760,"uid":113675,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T08:27:37.000Z","msg":"全香港都係咁<br />\n<br />\n只不過係另一種形式既VIP<br />\n<br />\n你估過時過節佢地唔洗買返d月餅同年糕咩<br />\n<br />\n條數係返度"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T08:59:40.000Z","msg":"點只月餅年糕<br />\n親戚D廢老擺生日酒 <br />\n早午晚都係同一間食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T10:01:33.000Z","msg":"岩呀 比我都會咁做 另類米飯班主"},{"pid":"286f97a222643bd989f553e7a527bad283291374","tid":757760,"uid":53798,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T11:46:07.000Z","msg":"咪玩啦, 餐廳有權唔做你生意<br />\n<br />\n不嬲無講要先後入場"},{"pid":"81d852f1ed47dab77687d52e1595f6f90adde01b","tid":757760,"uid":13257,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T11:49:56.000Z","msg":"呢樣真係全香港茶樓都係咁"},{"pid":"b46935cdc6c45825ce0d3915f818a4787502d897","tid":757760,"uid":166886,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T11:53:51.000Z","msg":"由於新加坡華人多，港式酒樓特別受歡迎，我在三十多年前已在新加坡開設了一間潮州酒樓，專門製作港式點心，酒樓聘請了兩位行內著名的港式點心師傅，他們均是具創意的人才，愛創造新款點心，如首創迷你月餅、楊枝甘露等。<br />\n<br />\n        新加坡的茶客通常也會訂枱。有一次，我們酒樓訂位部收到一位李小姐來電，訂了一張三位枱。酒樓向來不太喜歡招待三位枱，三位枱往往安排在比較近廁所角落位置。豈料那次的李小姐來到，夥計們見到才知「大鑊」了！原來她的爸爸是新加坡總理李顯龍、媽媽是總理夫人！<br />\n<br />\n        總理一家光顧，故意低調，沒有說出身份，夥計慌張得三魂不見了七魄，原本想立即安排他轉枱或移入房內，但李顯龍卻說不用，像平民百姓般坐在人群中，點了即叫即蒸的廣東點心。夥計們原打算補鑊，拿了些生果招呼站在門外的總理隨從，但他們非常清廉，一律不要。李顯龍吃完點心後，一家三口便埋單走人，一點便宜也不會拿，非常清廉。我真的非常欣賞他！<br />\n<br />\n        隔了不久，大家又再疏於防範，李小姐又再來電訂枱，夥計還是沒有留意，結果又是總理一家三口，他們照舊被安排坐在廁所角落位置的枱，低調地吃港式點心。又再捉蟲！幸好我們的酒樓向來着重服務，相信突擊也不會失禮。<br />\n<br />\n        聽行家說，除我們的酒家外，李總理還愛到四周的港式酒樓、茶餐廳用膳，下次到新加坡飲茶，不妨留意一下李顯龍會否在左近。<br />\n<a href=\"https://blog.stheadline.com/article/detail/731076\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblog.stheadline.com%2Farticle%2Fdetail%2F731076&d=5SQu4Df4Zm6QU7pBGlGX%2BL%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=4cd6f3cc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblog.stheadline.com%2Farticle%2Fdetail%2F731076&h=610a6521\" target=\"_blank\">https://blog.stheadline.com/article/detail/731076</a>"}]}